Trackimo + is the app for anyone who uses Trackimo devices to keep track of things they care about, like children, pets, vehicles, and personal items.

With "Trackimo +" you can:
- View real-time location
- Browse through travel history
- Get timely notifications when they arrive at a certain location
- Create and manage geo-zones to protect your loved ones
- Instantly share tracker location in case of emergency
- Send a beep sound if you lost a tracker
- Switch between Map View and Satellite View
